  "title": "Taller Forests",
  "description": "Makes trees in dense forests a little taller while staying vanilla. Helps with travelling.",
  "body": "# Description\nImproves visibility and mobility in forests by increasing the size of the trees, giving much more room below them, without completely redesigning the trees themselves.\n\nOther datapacks for the best forest experience: [Useful Structures](https://modrinth.com/datapack/useful-structures)\n\n# Versions\nSupports Java 1.18 - 26.1.2\n\n# Compatibility\nMay be incompatible with some worldgen datapacks due to them modifying the tree feature.\n\n  <a href=\"https://patreon.com/Nerd_1023?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink\"><img alt=\"patreon-singular\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/patreon-singular_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/Nerd-1023/Taller-Forests\"><img alt=\"github\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/m5AGYxRj3g\"><img alt=\"discord-singular\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\"></a>\n\n# Promotional Video\n  <iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\"\nsrc=\"https://youtube.com/embed/LhVpOss62Cc\">\n</iframe>",
